items.title: Harrowing details emerge after surfer killed by shark off popular beach
items.description: The surfer, who had a wife and young daughter, lost "a number of limbs" and his surfboard was broken in two, police said.

items.title: Palestinian gunmen kill six people in attack on Jerusalem bus stop
items.description: Israeli officials say two gunmen opened fire on a Jerusalem bus stop, killing six people and leaving seven others in serious condition.
